snippet: Moving to enforce cabinet discipline, President François Hollande on Tuesday fired Delphine Batho, the environment minister.
abstract: French Pres Francois Holland fires environment minister Delphine Batho in attempt at enforcing cabinet discipline; Batho had called proposed 2014 budget 'bad'.
lead_paragraph: Moving to enforce cabinet discipline, President François Hollande on Tuesday fired Delphine Batho, the environment minister.

headline.main: France: Political Guillotine Flashes, and Party Discipline Is Served
headline.print_headline: France: Political Guillotine Flashes, And Party Discipline Is Served
